steps.html_instructions:
Head west
May be closed at certain times or days
Keep left at the fork and merge onto Skyline Dr
Make a U-turn at Panorama Upper Parking Rd

Turn right onto US-340 N/US-522 N/N Shenandoah Ave
Continue to follow US-340 N/US-522 N

Take exit 1B to merge onto I-81 N toward Winchester
Passing through West Virginia
Entering Maryland
Take exit 4 to merge onto I-70 E toward Frederick
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit

Turn right onto MD-64 E/Jefferson Blvd
Continue to follow MD-64 E

Turn left onto MD-491/MacAfee Hill Rd
Continue to follow MacAfee Hill Rd

Continue onto Camp Ritchie Rd
Entering Pennsylvania

Slight right onto PA-16 E/Buchanan Trail E
Continue to follow PA-16 E

Merge onto PA-116 W/Fairfield Rd
Continue to follow PA-116 W
